<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
  <h1>隐私政策</h1>
  <p>感谢您使用本应用。我们非常重视您的隐私保护。</p>

  <h2>我们不会收集以下信息：</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>不会请求您的个人身份信息（如身份证号、家庭住址）</li>
    <li>不会请求或存储您的位置、通讯录或相册</li>
    <li>不会记录或出售您的任何行为数据</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>权限说明：</h2>
  <p>应用中可能使用麦克风、相机等系统权限，仅用于游戏内的互动功能，所有信息处理仅在设备本地进行，不上传至服务器。</p>

  <h2>第三方服务说明：</h2>
  <p>我们可能会集成 Apple Game Center、Firebase 或类似服务，仅用于游戏登录与统计分析，不涉及用户身份识别。</p>

  <h2>政策更新：</h2>
  <p>如本隐私政策有更新，我们会在此页面及时公布。</p>

  <hr />

  <h1>Privacy Policy (EN)</h1>
  <p>Thank you for using our app. Your privacy is important to us.</p>

  <h2>What We Don't Collect:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No personal information like ID numbers or addresses</li>
    <li>No contact lists, photos, or precise location</li>
    <li>No behavior or activity tracking for sale</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Permissions:</h2>
  <p>Permissions (e.g. microphone, camera) may be used for in-app gameplay only. All data is kept locally and not uploaded.</p>

  <h2>Third-party SDKs:</h2>
  <p>We may use Apple Game Center or Firebase for basic services, without accessing or storing personal identity data.</p>

  <h2>Updates:</h2>
  <p>Any changes will be published on this page.</p>
